//*  HOURGLASS 2000 VERSION 3.3 INTEGRATION PATCH FOR LE/370 V1R9.
//*  HOURGLASS 2000 VERSION 4.1 INTEGRATION PATCH FOR LE/370 V1R9.
//*  HOURGLASS 2000 VERSION 5.0 INTEGRATION PATCH FOR LE/370 V1R9.
//*
