//*******************************************************************
//*                 BC0THOR.PDS.JCL(PRTBKMGR)                       *
//* PRINT A BOOK MANAGER FILE CREATED IN A MAINFRAME BOOKMANAGER    *
//* SESSION USING THE SERVICES MENU OPTION, 2 PRINT, 1 TOPICS ONLY, *
//* FROM TOPIC CONTENTS, THROUGH TOPIC INDEX, PK PRINT AND KEEP.    *
//* ON COMPLETION, PURGE THE JOB FROM SDSF AND SUBMIT THIS JOB TO   *
//* PRINT THE DISK DATASET CREATED ABOVE.
//*******************************************************************
