//*********************************************************************
//*                   BC0THOR.PDS.JCL(SMFDSNV1)                       *
//*********************************************************************
//* SELECTS SMF TYPE 17,18,60,62, AND 64 FOR DSNAME GIVEN IN READER1. *
//* OUTPUT MAY BE FED INTO SMFDSNV2                                   *
