//*******************************************************************
//*                 BC0THOR.PDS.JCL(SMPLIST)                        *
//* WRITES A FILE OF INFO FROM AN SMP CSI, ONE LINE PER SYSMOD.     *
//* CONTROL CARDS MAY BE USED TO TAILOR THE OUTPUT. SEE COMMENTS IN *
//* THE SOURCE PROGRAM FOR DETAILS.                                 *
