//* SOURCE PROGRAM IS BC0THOR.PDS.COBOL(XXXXXXXX)                   *
//* OUTPUT LOAD MODULE IS BC0THOR.LOAD.LOAD(XXXXXXXX)               *
//*******************************************************************
//*------------------------------------------------------------------
